citeinfo.origin: Originator -- the name of an organization or individual that developed the data set; if not provided, leave blank
citeinfo.pubdate: Publication Date -- the date when the data set is published or otherwise made available for release; if not provided, leave blank
citeinfo.title: (GISIRequired) Title -- the name by which the data set is known
citeinfo.onlink: Organization main website URL; if not provided, leave blank

descript.abstract: (GISIRequired) A brief description of the dataset.
descript.purpose: A brief description of the purpose of the dataset; if not provided, leave blank

sngdate.caldate: Time Period of Content -- information about the date; if not provided, then leave blank

timeperd.current: Currentness Reference -- the basis on which the time period of content information is determined. Domain: "ground condition" "publication date"; if blank GISI will use "publication date"

status.progress: (GISIRequired) Progress -- the state of the data set. Domain: "Complete" "In work" "Planned"; if blank, GISI will use "Complete"
status.update: Maintenance and Update Frequency -- the frequency with which changes and additions are made to the data set after the initial data set is completed. Domain: "Continually" "Daily" "Weekly" "Monthly" "Annually" "Unknown" "As needed" "Irregular" "None planned"; if not provided, then leave blank

bounding.westbc: [[westbc] from imported metadata, if provided; if not provided, GISI will generate from account geography]
bounding.eastbc: [[eastbc] from imported metadata, if provided; if not provided, GISI will generate from account geography]
bounding.northbc: [[northbc] from imported metadata, if provided; if not provided, GISI will generate from account geography]
bounding.southbc: [[southbc] from imported metadata, if provided; GISI will generate from account geography]

theme.themekt: Theme Keyword Thesaurus -- reference to a formally registered thesaurus or a similar authoritative source of theme keywords; if not provided, then Domain: "None"
theme.themekey: (repeatable element)-1 Theme Keyword -- common-use word or phrase used to describe the subject of the data set; if not provided, then leave blank

place.placekt: Place Keyword Thesaurus -- reference to a formally registered thesaurus or a similar authoritative source of place keywords; if not provided, then Domain: "None"
place.placekey: (repeatable element)-1 Place Keyword -- the geographic name of a location covered by a data set; if not provided, then leave blank

idinfo.accconst: Access Constraints -- restrictions and legal prerequisites for accessing the data set. These include any access constraints applied to assure the protection of privacy or intellectual property, and any special restrictions or limitations on obtaining the data set; if not provided then Domain: "None" or leave blank.
idinfo.useconst: Use Constraints -- restrictions and legal prerequisites for using the data set after access is granted. These include any use constraints applied to assure the protection of privacy or intellectual property, and any special restrictions or limitations on using the data set; if not provided then Domain: "None" or leave blank.

distinfo.distliab: Distribution Liability -- statement of the liability assumed by the distributor; if not provided, then Domain: "None" or leave blank
